| 6 | No error handling middleware | 🟠 Medium | A05 – Security Misconfiguration |
| 7 | Health endpoint info disclosure | 🟡 Low | A05 – Security Misconfiguration |
| 8 | Listening on all interfaces | 🟡 Low | A05 – Security Misconfiguration |
| 9 | No request/security logging | 🟡 Low | A09 – Security Logging Failures |
| 10 | No HTTPS enforcement | 🟡 Low | A02 – Cryptographic Failures |

