| Priority | Finding | Effort |
|---|---|---|
| 🔴 1 | Add authentication to `/users` | Low |
| 🔴 2 | Remove hardcoded PII | Low |
| 🟠 3 | Add `helmet` security headers | Trivial |
| 🟠 4 | Add rate limiting | Low |
| 🟠 5 | Strip timestamp from `/health` | Trivial |
| 🟡 6 | Add body parsing + input validation middleware | Low |
| 🟡 7 | Configure CORS explicitly | Low |
| 🟡 8 | Read port from environment | Trivial |

