app.use(helmet()); // Sets X-Content-Type-Options, X-Frame-Options, HSTS, etc.
app.disable('x-powered-by'); // Don't advertise your stack
```

---

### 🟠 MEDIUM — [A05] Security Misconfiguration: No Rate Limiting

The `/users` and `/health` endpoints have **no rate limiting**. This enables brute-force, enumeration, and denial-of-service attacks.

**Recommendation:** Add `express-rate-limit`:

```js
